00083 void Whirlpool::TruncatedFinal(byte *hash, size_t size)
00084 {
00085         ThrowIfInvalidTruncatedSize(size);
00086 
00087         PadLastBlock(32);
00088         CorrectEndianess(m_data, m_data, 32);
00089 
00090         m_data[m_data.size()-4] = 0;
00091         m_data[m_data.size()-3] = 0;
00092         m_data[m_data.size()-2] = GetBitCountHi();
00093         m_data[m_data.size()-1] = GetBitCountLo();
00094 
00095         Transform(m_state, m_data);
00096         CorrectEndianess(m_state, m_state, DigestSize());
00097         memcpy(hash, m_state, size);
00098 
00099         Restart();              // reinit for next use
00100 }
